&lt;p&gt;- 3–4 years of experience performing IT audits, with a focus on ITGC and application controls&lt;br&gt;- Strong working knowledge of SOC 2 and related frameworks&lt;br&gt;- Bachelor’s degree in Accounting, MIS, Cybersecurity, or a related field&lt;br&gt;- Strong client communication and project management skills&lt;br&gt;- Bilingual in English required&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Experience with GRC tools (e.g., Vanta, Drata, Secureframe)&lt;br&gt;- Familiarity with cloud environments such as AWS, Azure, or GCP&lt;br&gt;- Progress toward CISA, CPA, CISSP, ISO 27001 Lead Auditor&lt;/p&gt;
